                "typeId": 1,
                "questionText": "Cho tam giác <i>ABC</i> và các điểm <i>M, N</i> lần lượt nằm trên các cạnh <i>AB, AC</i> sao cho <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/c4ce0574-f1b4-4304-bfc7-f7cc6e5a0e34.png\"/>\n<br>a) Chứng minh rằng <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/e5383136-9305-4e6d-af7b-aaf8513a8795.png\"/>\n<br>b) Chứng minh rằng <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/76969075-615e-47da-9f43-c164b510f1d1.png\"/>\n<br>c) Gọi <i>O</i> là giao điểm của <i>BN</i> và <i>CM</i>. Chứng minh rằng <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/71994eea-ba71-4104-b091-c179be8844eb.png\"/>\n",
                "answer": "<img src=\"https://asset.moon.vn/img/chat/large/2026/1/1a1327be-7421-42fe-81a7-edcf48c5fe22.jpg\" data-filename=\"\" style=\"max-width: 600px; height: auto;\"><br>a) Hai tam giác <i>AMN</i> và <i>ACB</i> có góc <i>MAN</i> = góc<i> CAB</i> (góc chung), <i>AMN </i>= góc <i>ACB</i>(gt) <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/64cf3ad6-e2c9-4fd8-bca2-df806fbb4566.png\"/>\n<br>b) Vì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/121bd207-02b8-4851-ab09-4e4f5af9115d.png\"/> nên ta có <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/86fbb29e-1220-4899-89f8-c5710e2d09ca.png\"/> suy ra <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/01d9b07f-e8ea-434c-9130-480b6a9fc8b8.png\"/>\n<br>Xét <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/fb976bd5-f876-42ac-8be8-a0350beae2f8.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/3a7a69cd-7672-4720-8f7e-42f9f67a4d2e.png\"/> ta có góc <i>BAN</i> = góc <i>CAM</i> (góc chung), <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/2282013b-93ed-4400-ac22-c6b67927c8e1.png\"/> (chứng minh trên) <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/64763beb-02ac-4265-9e2f-8ac035c7bc88.png\"/> (c.g.c)\n<br>c) <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/e20f7076-97a0-4f57-8b6e-1dd68c34faa4.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/ccf725bb-5d25-4c82-92a4-6fe2abcabd3f.png\"/> ta có góc MOB = góc ABN = góc <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/a9aa5d37-05c7-46ae-9052-ba690cf7705e.png\"/> (vì <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/04aeb551-2a5c-425b-aa12-33af38146cd2.png\"/>), góc <i>MON</i> = góc NOC (hai góc đối đỉnh) <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/ff221416-d705-4a28-b854-a958877a63e3.png\"/> (g.g).\n<br>Do đó <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/1d1eac6a-a722-44b1-9d91-f4f67e49eec2.png\"/> hay <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/acb7604d-925b-4967-9ce0-5be5156735d1.png\"/>\n<br>Xét <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/ed822819-8ea8-46cf-ba35-663af7829dae.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/33626896-6eb4-4ef6-8d41-c650d38c509f.png\"/> ta có <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/a794e313-d77c-46cd-b60a-0e846463e683.png\"/> góc <i>MON</i> = góc <i>BOC</i> (đối đỉnh). Vậy <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/70a617bb-92d6-41b8-aba2-74572e21e921.png\"/> (c.g.c).\n",
